graph TD
    subgraph Read ["On every read"]
        R1[Fetch from SQLite/IndexedDB] --> R2[Verify checksum]
        R2 -->|Mismatch| R3[Attempt recovery]
        R3 --> R3a[Fallback to WAL]
        R3 --> R3b[Downshift schema version]
        R3 --> R3c[Salvage what is readable]
    end

    subgraph Write ["On every write"]
        W1[Compute + store checksum] --> W2[Log to WAL before commit]
        W2 --> W3[Atomic append]
        W3 --> W4[Verify write succeeded]
    end
